  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to develop an emergency electroencephalogram (EEG) device,
      StatNet, that can be placed quickly by minimally-trained personnel and interpreted remotely
      for rapid identification of seizures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
